item.title: CVE-2022-34808|2024-08-03T09:22:09.877Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20cisco%20spark%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Cisco Spark Plugin 1.1.1 and earlier stores bearer tokens unencrypted in its global configuration file on the Jenkins controller where they can be viewed by users with access to the Jenkins controller file system.
